To run the dataset for Neural machine translation :

Install Open-NMT-py in a GPU environment from:  https://github.com/OpenNMT/OpenNMT-py.git
with command 
#pip install OpenNMT-py
git clone https://github.com/OpenNMT/OpenNMT-py.git
cd OpenNMT-py
pip install -e .

Steps:
create: src-train.txt, src-test.txt, src-valid.txt, tgt-train.txt, tgt-valid.txt, tgt-test.txt 
Pre-Process the Source and Target files
Train
and Translate 


Download pretrained models from: https://opennmt.net/Models-py/
